==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{lb|en|grammar}} A [[tense]] used to describe something that happened in the past, formed by the inflection of a single word, without any auxiliary verb such as ''be'' or ''have''.

====Synonyms====
* {{sense|grammar}} {{l|en|preterite}}, {{l|en|preterit}}

